title: Keep Connecting With Your Middle-Schooler
itunes:author: Guests: Jonathan Catherman, Reed Catherman, and Cole Catherman.
itunes:summary: Is your middle-schooler pushing you away? John and Danny demystify the emotions behind your child's behavior. Featuring Jonathan Catherman, Reed Catherman, and Cole Catherman. Find us online at focusonthefamily.com/parentingpodcast or call 1-800-A-FAMILY.
